00:00:13.481 --> 00:00:17.928
Hi...Welcome to Aha emi ruchi...!!!

00:00:27.248 --> 00:00:28.097
What are you cooking for us today...

00:00:28.164 --> 00:00:29.051
Macaroni Kheer

00:00:37.435 --> 00:00:39.221
Ingredients required to cook Macaroni kheer:

00:00:39.914 --> 00:00:44.500
Macaroni, Milkmaid, Milk, Cashew nuts and Ghee

00:00:45.295 --> 00:00:49.678
Let us now see...how to cook macaroni kheer...

00:00:57.627 --> 00:01:00.730
Firstly, boil some water in a bowl

00:01:01.307 --> 00:01:05.576
Take 2 cups of water for 1 cup of macaroni

00:01:18.301 --> 00:01:22.495
Macaronies are of different shapes

00:01:23.924 --> 00:01:27.854
These are like shells

00:01:46.652 --> 00:01:51.717
Add the macaroni after the water is boiled

00:01:52.194 --> 00:01:57.756
Let it cook for 10 minutes

00:02:24.299 --> 00:02:29.015
After the macaroni is cooked, Add 1 spoon ghee...

00:02:35.283 --> 00:02:39.920
Add 1 cup of milkmaid

00:02:46.699 --> 00:02:55.459
We are not using sugar because milkmaid is already sweet...

00:03:07.297 --> 00:03:10.013
Let it cook for 2 minutes...

00:03:16.650 --> 00:03:21.402
Add 1/2 cup of milk and mix properly

00:03:23.931 --> 00:03:32.529
Cook till a layer of cream is formed...

00:03:50.372 --> 00:03:55.360
In another bowl...heat some ghee

00:03:56.293 --> 00:04:04.842
Fry some cashew nuts and add them in the kheer

00:04:15.010 --> 00:04:22.695
Add sugar powder if required

00:04:30.900 --> 00:04:41.746
Serve it in a bowl...

